Revision history for C dirq:

???	???
	* Added CC and CFLAGS support to the configure script.
	* Added DIRQ_VERSION_* constants to dirq.h.

0.4	Thu Nov 10 2016
	* Added pkg-config support.

0.3	Tue Jan 26 2016
	* Fixed incorrect memory handling resulting in segfaults.
	* First version released on GitHub.

0.2	Wed Jan 13 2016
	* Added dirq_copy(), dirq_get_size() and dirq_touch().
	* Improved the randomness of the default rndhex.
	* Added a --random option to dqt.
	* Added shared library support.

0.1	Fri Jun 14 2013
	* First packaged version.
